; Regression test for issue #1034: --group-by and --pivot together
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1034
;
; When --group-by and --pivot were used together, only the first group's
; output appeared and subsequent groups (including their titles) were
; silently dropped.  Root cause: account_t::clear_xdata() skipped
; ACCOUNT_TEMP children, leaving the family_details cache populated with a
; stale (zero) total for accounts under the pivot's temp parent.  In the
; second group, mark_accounts then read the cached zero from the pivoted
; leaves, failed the display predicate, and produced no output.

2011-01-01 * Opening balance
    Assets:Cash                               25.00 GBP
    Equity:Opening balance                   -25.00 GBP

2011-02-01 * Sell to customer AAA
    ; Customer: AAA
    ; Invoice: 101
    Assets:Receivables                        10.00 GBP
    Income:Sale                              -10.00 GBP

2011-02-02 * Sell to customer BBB
    ; Customer: BBB
    ; Invoice: 102
    Assets:Receivables                        11.00 GBP
    Income:Sale                              -11.00 GBP

2011-02-03 * Sell to customer AAA
    ; Customer: AAA
    ; Invoice: 103
    Assets:Receivables                        12.00 GBP
    Income:Sale                              -12.00 GBP

2011-02-04 * Sell to customer AAA
    ; Customer: AAA
    ; Invoice: 104
    Assets:Receivables                        15.00 GBP
    Income:Sale                              -15.00 GBP

2011-02-03 * Money received from customer AAA for invoice 101
    ; Customer: AAA
    ; Invoice: 101
    Assets:Cash                               10.00 GBP
    Assets:Receivables                       -10.00 GBP

; --group-by alone groups by Customer tag.
test bal assets:receiv --group-by "tag('Customer')"
AAA
           27.00 GBP  Assets:Receivables

BBB
           11.00 GBP  Assets:Receivables
end test

; --pivot alone groups receivables under their Invoice tag.
test bal assets:receiv --pivot Invoice
           38.00 GBP  Invoice
           11.00 GBP    102:Assets:Receivables
           12.00 GBP    103:Assets:Receivables
           15.00 GBP    104:Assets:Receivables
--------------------
           38.00 GBP
end test

; --group-by combined with --pivot must show every group that has a
; matching posting, with the pivoted account hierarchy underneath each
; group's title.  Before the fix, BBB's group was silently dropped.
test bal assets:receiv --group-by "tag('Customer')" --pivot Invoice
AAA
           27.00 GBP  Invoice
           12.00 GBP    103:Assets:Receivables
           15.00 GBP    104:Assets:Receivables
--------------------
           27.00 GBP

BBB
           11.00 GBP  Invoice:102:Assets:Receivables
end test

; The same combination must work for register reports as well.
test reg assets:receiv --group-by "tag('Customer')" --pivot Invoice
AAA
11-Feb-01 Sell to customer AAA  In:10:Asse:Receivables    10.00 GBP    10.00 GBP
11-Feb-03 Sell to customer AAA  In:10:Asse:Receivables    12.00 GBP    22.00 GBP
11-Feb-04 Sell to customer AAA  In:10:Asse:Receivables    15.00 GBP    37.00 GBP
11-Feb-03 Money received from.. In:10:Asse:Receivables   -10.00 GBP    27.00 GBP

BBB
11-Feb-02 Sell to customer BBB  In:10:Asse:Receivables    11.00 GBP    11.00 GBP
end test
